Name: Financial CS Revenue

Caption.String: Subscription revenue is from payments made to the project by up to four subscriber classes. Revenue from each subscriber class may be from any combination of up-front, annual, or generation payments. Subscription revenue is in addition to any project revenue defined on the Revenue page.

Tool Tip.String: Click Value/Sched to switch between a single value with an escalation rate and annual values over the analysis period.
